  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK438">
<l>paṟṟuḷḷa meṉṉu mivaṟaṉmai yeṟṟuḷḷu</l>
<l>meṇṇap paṭuvatoṉ ṟaṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Griping avarice is not to be reckoned as one among other faults (it stands alone - greater than all).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
